							<div class="comment_ct">
								<P class=Title>chong tac duong</P>
<P class=Normal>Theo toi y kien cua ban khong kha thi vi khong bam sat vao thuc te cuoc song, dua vao nhung dieu cu the sau day. </P>
<P class=Normal>Diem 5- Nhung nguoi thuc su can thiet tham gia giao thong vao gio cao diem thi phai dong phi phu hop voi xu the phat trien cua xa hoi...... thua ban chung toi cung khong muon xong ra duong vao gio cao diem de choi ma de lam nhung viec can lam cho gia dinh, con cai va muu sinh nua voi dong luong cong chuc com hien nay da cong nhieu khoan phi vo ly roi bay gio ban con muon chung toi phai tra them mot khoan phi nua vi da tham gia giao thong vao gio cao diem u, nhu vay thue chong len thue, phi chong len phi.</P>
<P class=Normal>Dieu 2 : Khuyen khich CBCNV den co quan truoc 7 h sang va ve muon hon, tam huyet hon neu co the.</P>
<P class=Normal>Neu chung toi den co quan truoc 7 h vay con cai va nhung nguoi phu thuoc cua chung toi phai day tu may gio sang de di cung bo me den truong lop va chung toi se o dau khi co quan truong hoc chua mo cua, ca nha ngoi quan ca phe doi a. buoi toi cung the, ban muon chung toi het gio cao diem moi ve de giam un tac giao thong, vay con chung toi het gio hoc se dung bo vo o cong truong den may gio moi duoc don ve nha cho an, con di hoc them, di chua benh, lam bai tap o nha.......</P>
<P class=Normal>Toi chi dua ra vai y kien nhu vay de ban suy nghi them khi dua ra mot giai phap lien quan den toan xa hoi con cac dieu khac cac anh cac chi da dua ra y kien roi . </P>
<P class=Normal><I>( Lan an )</I></P>
